Problem Description:            

There are two parts to this assignment. The first involves modifying
distributed Hey to use threads. The second part involves some simple 
performance comparisons between processes and threads. The Performance 
section describes the comparisons you are to do.

Answers:                        NA

How to build the program:       make

How to run the program:         
	hey_server    
        hey <host>
For Benchmark tesing run:
	bench
